PrecisReappointment of GAIL COOK-BENNETT, of Etobicoke, Ontario, as a director of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a period ending October 26, 2008; and designation of GAIL COOK-BENNETT as Chairperson of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board to hold office during good behaviour for a period ending October 26, 2008.
